OL,3,CJersey bus company 'seriously
OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FThe head of Jersey's bus service says
OL,7,Fthe company would "seriously consider"
OL,8,Fgoing cashless.
OL,10,FKevin Hart told a scrutiny panel of
OL,11,Fpoliticians that Liberty Bus would
OL,12,Fsave #65,000 a year if it stopped
OL,13,Fhandling money and moved to
OL,14,Fcontactless-only card transactions,
OL,15,Fwhich already makes up most payments
OL,16,Falongside travel passes and mobile
OL,17,Ftickets.
