OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FMr Hart says just 2.5% of total sales
OL,7,Fare made in cash and they only receive
OL,8,Faround 72p for every #1 spent due to
OL,9,Fadmin costs.
OL,11,FIf Liberty Bus goes cashless, it would
OL,12,Ffollow Guernsey buses which stopped
OL,13,Fhandling money in July 2021.
OL,15,FMr Hart explains: "It's something we
OL,16,Fwould need to seriously consider when
OL,17,Fyou look at the costs involved in
OL,18,Fhandling cash.
