OL,3,CJersey bus company 'seriously
OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,F"You've got the cost of the machines
OL,7,Fto count it, the individuals to bag it
OL,8,Fup, the security to collect the cash,
OL,9,Fthe bank charges as well, so there's a
OL,10,Fwhole process where the more cash we
OL,11,Ftake, the higher our costs."
OL,13,FThe Director reassures customers that
OL,14,FLiberty Bus is "quite happy" taking
OL,15,Fcash but is encouraging them to use
OL,16,Falternatives where possible.
OL,18,FCurrently, the bus service must take
OL,19,Fcash payments due to contractual
OL,20,Fobligations set by Jersey's government.
