OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FHowever, the Economic and
OL,7,FInternational Affairs Scrutiny Panel
OL,8,Fare speaking to businesses to
OL,9,Funderstand whether they want cash
OL,10,Fprotected or continue to be naturally
OL,11,Fphased out of society.
OL,13,FThe prospect of Jersey phasing out
OL,14,Fcash payments has received pushback
OL,15,Ffrom some businesses and politicians.
OL,17,FIn June, Sustainable Economic
OL,18,FDevelopment Minister Kirsten Morel
OL,19,Ftold ITV Channel that he would bring
OL,20,Fforward a proposal to protect cash
OL,21,Fpayments on the island.
