OL,3,CJersey bus company 'seriously
OL,4,Cconsiders' ending cash payments
OL,6,FAt the time, he explained: "It's my
OL,7,Fbelief that we shouldn't lose cash and
OL,8,Fthat's why I'm thinking of bringing a
OL,9,Fproposition to ensure cash is
OL,10,Fmaintained in Jersey.
OL,12,F"It can be cheaper and easier for
OL,13,Fbanks and businesses (to do card
OL,14,Ftransactions), but their cost savings
OL,15,Fshouldn't be at the expense of our
OL,16,Fchoice and freedom."
OL,18,FThe issue of whether businesses should
OL,19,Fbe obligied to accept cash payments is
OL,20,Fcontroversial.
